			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">%M is the pet.
<br />

<br />
I recall, from a looooong time ago, trying
<br />

<br />
/assist %M
<br />

<br />
in a hotkey, but it seemed that somehow it got stuck on my "first" pet's name and didn't update when I had subsequent pets in a play session. I haven't checked to see if that approach is still "buggy" these days.
<br />

<br />
F1 selects yourself, then toggles between you and your pet.
<br />

<br />
My "assist pet" "hotkey" is [F1] [F1] [nomal assist hotkey]<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Elementalist Itchyban of Veeshan</a>
<br />
"Nothing to see here. Move along. Move along." 
<br />
"These are not the droids you are looking for."</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
