<br />

<br />
I use these 2 lines:
<br />

<br />
/pet target (targets your pet)
<br />
/assist
<br />

<br />
In this case you dont need to change pet names in the hotbutton, each time a new pet comes up. I made this actually to ease the looting of the whirlwind mobs in LdoN Addies, as looting them by mouseclick could be a pain.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
