				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Itchy, if your pet died (or you camped) without zoning it seems it stays with the first pet name. If you suspend a pet and use a new one, it keeps the first pet's name. I think it has to do with changing zones while you still have an active pet although I have not tested this extensively. Your pet is counted as alive still if you do not kill him prior to gating, zoning or camping (though with the zoning pets and suspend minion 3 zoning is no longer a factor imo). I on minor occassion get the pet name problem where I have to use %m again after clearing my previous pet's name.
