			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Bastler wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Khauruk wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Uhh...this probably sounds stupid, but what's the command to assist a pet?  I have it for my BST, but can't figure it out for my mage.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
I use these 2 lines:
<br />

<br />
/pet target (targets your pet)
<br />
/assist
<br />

<br />
In this case you dont need to change pet names in the hotbutton, each time a new pet comes up. I made this actually to ease the looting of the whirlwind mobs in LdoN Addies, as looting them by mouseclick could be a pain.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
The /assist name is basically, 
<br />
/target [name] 
<br />
/assist.  
<br />

<br />
/target [name] fails if you "can't see your target"  I have been siting next to a person while waiting for a raid to start and issued /target [name] and have it return the "can't see name" error message.  
<br />

<br />
The 
<br />
/pet target
<br />
/assist 
<br />
method is much preferred because /pet target always targets your pet and /assist range is much larger than the /target range.
<br />

<br />
My macro actually looks like
<br />
/pet target
<br />
/1 Targeting %t
<br />
/assist.
<br />

<br />
Since the huge macro changes made last year, I have found that the target functions and especially the assist functions don't always finish before the next macro line is excuted.  I know this because sometimes the /1 Targeting %t message gives me the wrong target.  By putting the /1 Targeting %t, it delays the third line enough to make sure you pet is targeted before you assist.<br />_________________<br />Dabrighter Blazemeister
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=449337" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=449337</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
