				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have also made a new LOOT key.
<br />

<br />
/pet target
<br />
/pause 1
<br />
/assist
<br />
/pause 1
<br />
/loot
<br />

<br />
When a mob dies, pet still has the corpse of mob on its target until you tell it to attack something else.  So it makes for fast, easy looting without having to click on corpses.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4796" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #FF0000"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: normal">Lord Zacatac Soulwanderer</a></span></span></span>
